And, uh,

02:29.483 --> 02:31.318
Friday, I'm going to meet
with my sponsor and she will

02:31.318 --> 02:33.654
talk me down off the ledge
about that IVF appointment,

02:33.654 --> 02:36.490
and on the weekend I hang out
with Vinny and the boys.

02:36.490 --> 02:38.859
They're this incredible group
of lesbians.

02:38.859 --> 02:39.960
