02:50.537 --> 02:52.272
‐And the ones that didn't...
‐Well, their loss, right?

02:52.272 --> 02:53.640
(scoffs)
God, no. Mine.

02:53.640 --> 02:55.542
Uh‐huh.

02:55.542 --> 02:58.011
And, uh, these amends‐‐
they're just like

02:58.011 --> 03:00.514
‐a big apology, right?
‐No.

03:00.514 --> 03:02.182
Uh, an apology is words.

03:02.182 --> 03:03.850
An amends is action.

03:03.850 --> 03:05.619
"I'm‐I'm sorry" is like
jumping over a puddle.

03:05.619 --> 03:08.188
An amends is rebuilding
a bridge you blew up.

03:08.188 --> 03:09.990
