give an amends to Brit.

03:09.990 --> 03:12.826
No, no, no, no, no.
It's way too early for amends.

03:12.826 --> 03:16.029
‐You cannot do that
until you've changed.
‐Yeah, but I have changed.

03:16.029 --> 03:18.899
‐(short chuckle)
‐I have. I make my bed, I floss,

03:18.899 --> 03:20.000
‐I do all the stuff.
‐Sam, listen,

03:20.000 --> 03:21.868
the steps are in order
for a reason.

03:21.868 --> 03:23.670
Let's just stay away from people

03:23.670 --> 03:25.672
and places that we find
triggering right now.

03:25.672 --> 03:27.307
Got it.
No triggers.

03:27.307 --> 03:28.308
Very good.

03:28.308 --> 03:29.576
(phone vibrates)

03:29.576 --> 03:31.378
All right.

03:31.378 --> 03:33.747
‐Have fun with Vinny
and the boys.
‐No triggers.

03:35.615 --> 03:37.417
