04:07.414 --> 04:09.015
And, like I said‐‐

04:09.015 --> 04:12.753
‐judgy.
‐Yeah, you seem super normal.

04:12.753 --> 04:14.121
Samantha...

04:14.121 --> 04:15.255
Hmm?

04:15.255 --> 04:16.389
I haven't shared

04:16.389 --> 04:19.025
