04:29.870 --> 04:32.739
and nobody knows
what digital means anyway.

04:32.739 --> 04:36.076
Uh‐huh. Yeah, sure, or you
could just tell them the truth

04:36.076 --> 04:37.878
'cause I'm about to get
my 30‐day chip

04:37.878 --> 04:40.180
and it's, like,
kind of a big deal, so...

04:40.180 --> 04:41.348
And, of course,

04:41.348 --> 04:42.849
