06:26.786 --> 06:28.421
Oh, my God.

06:28.421 --> 06:30.523
Hey, Joel.

06:30.523 --> 06:32.626
Sam.
What are you doing here?

06:32.626 --> 06:34.127
Oh, this is my godson, Zacky.

06:34.127 --> 06:35.195
We're here to skate.

06:35.195 --> 06:37.197
