06:50.677 --> 06:51.711
Three. Cool.

06:52.746 --> 06:55.248
‐So, you good?
‐Yeah.

06:55.248 --> 06:57.250
I'm actually glad to see you.

06:57.250 --> 06:59.152
You know, after we ran into you
at the grocery store

06:59.152 --> 07:02.122
‐I‐I just started feeling bad.
‐Why?

07:02.122 --> 07:04.557
'Cause it was awkward.
I mean, it's weird to see

07:04.557 --> 07:05.825
