your whole life

07:05.825 --> 07:07.227
and ask them for deli meat.

07:07.227 --> 07:10.063
Yeah. Well, try serving
someone deli meat

07:10.063 --> 07:12.299
you've known your whole life.
It's actually way worse.

07:12.299 --> 07:14.567
Well, this is feeling
pretty good right now.

07:14.567 --> 07:16.503
‐It is. It's a bit...
a bit better, yeah.
‐Less awkward.

07:16.503 --> 07:19.706
‐You here by yourself?
‐Uh, no, I came with Brit.

07:19.706 --> 07:21.241
Oh, Brit's here.

07:21.241 --> 07:23.443
Yeah, it's actually
her birthday.

07:23.443 --> 07:24.878
But...

07:24.878 --> 07:26.446
You already know that.
Okay,

07:26.446 --> 07:28.481
no.
I‐I can't get involved

07:28.481 --> 07:29.816
with the two of you, all right?
Please don't

07:29.816 --> 07:31.084
‐do this on her birthday.
‐It's a good thing.

07:31.084 --> 07:32.485
I'm here to make an amends.

07:32.485 --> 07:34.254
Sam...

07:34.254 --> 07:36.656
with all due respect, uh...

07:36.656 --> 07:39.426
